"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4pApKaEiZHS681oVefy6u.png?height=360&width=1080)\\n\\nSTO通过对股票、债券和商品等传统投资类型进行代币化，弥合了传统货币市场与新数字货币时代之间的差距。资产的代币化是表达和管理资产的最强大的方式之一，它以代币的形式直接在区块链上表示。这允许在区块链上自动协调和验证的无错误交易，无需人工调解。STO是一种证券型代币产品，其运作方式与ICO相同，不同之处在于投资者的资金是通过证券型代币而非传统的加密货币来表示的。\\n\\n全球首家DeFiAMM和流动性池提供商\\n\\n一个平台，IXSwap(IXS)全力挖掘证券代币的潜力，这就是为什么它完全致力于开发一个专门构建的STODeFi平台，用户可以在其中交易和投资代币化股票以及手推车，贷款和做市商具有巨大的潜在回报。\\n\\n区块链上的借贷与投资者以前从事的任何事情都不一样。它为寻求高收益和被动收入带来了无与伦比的机会。对于借款，客户无需坐在借款人对面或签署任何文件，因为区块链为他们提供了一种无需信任的方法来进行此类交易，因为部署了智能合约。\\n\\nIXSwap是一个AMM，一个面向STO和TSO的自动化做市商和流动性池平台，其主要目标是为这个领域带来深度流动性。IXSwap将运行的流动性池包括一个用于托管资产（由第3方托管人监督流程）和一个用于非托管资产（用户可以抵押自己的代币以享受一定比例的费用）。\\n\\nIXSwap为用户提供损失保险，将8%的资金、5%的交易费用和50%的罚款分配给保险基金。整个协议以原生IXS令牌为核心。它被分发给用户以获得奖励和忠诚度，并且还有自己的池，以及作为InvestaXCEX平台的支付代币。\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\nSTO closes the gap between the traditional money market and the new digital money era by tokenizing traditional investment types such as stocks, bonds and commodities. Asset tokenization is one of the most powerful ways to express and manage assets. It is expressed directly on the blockchain in the form of tokens. This allows error free transactions to be automatically coordinated and verified on the blockchain without manual mediation. Sto is a security token product, and its operation mode is the same as ICO. The difference is that investors' funds are expressed through security tokens rather than traditional cryptocurrencies.\\n\\nThe world's first defiamm and liquidity pool provider\\n\\nOne platform, ixswap (IXS), tries its best to tap the potential of securities tokens, which is why it is fully committed to developing a specially built stodefi platform in which users can trade and invest in token stocks, trolleys, loans and market makers, with huge potential returns.\\n\\nLending on the blockchain is different from anything investors have done before. It provides unparalleled opportunities for seeking high returns and passive income. For borrowing, customers do not need to sit opposite the borrower or sign any documents, because blockchain provides them with a way to conduct such transactions without trust, because smart contracts are deployed.\\n\\nIxswap is an AMM, an automated market maker and liquidity pool platform for sto and Tso. Its main goal is to bring deep liquidity to this field. The liquidity pool ixswap will run includes one for managed assets (the process is supervised by a third-party custodian) and one for unmanaged assets (users can mortgage their own tokens to enjoy a certain proportion of fees).\\n\\nIxswap provides loss insurance for users and allocates 8% of funds, 5% of transaction costs and 50% of fines to the insurance fund. The whole protocol takes the native IXS token as the core. It is distributed to users for rewards and loyalty, and has its own pool, as well as a payment token for the investaxcex platform.\",\"timestamp\":1639034539,\"title\":\"传统金融市场与加密代币化之间的桥梁_IXSWAP\"},\"digest\":\"saaVSoRJM_ErfyMYjWCJ-6jD4IMJ_wHJOsB-FqqJyIQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE671e705Bf5b7A74CD18C4aF4a8d6766B1F52cBf\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"maY7YkpZGqJmVhCURWwfqETeLY-qwyY-hQIaJUV_QGU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"kuPEc2Wr2AOWCjTB2Odep553BUM8Mht8S9lANqipBDk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"0-xp_vefU8b2DazeKsAfWF0S3VmQkSIzE31YzhAGv1H3BscT7pXHgFpAxsg_Uo7oO2VUihisSqkZrR4x0Ru9wQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xbb43eaf6162e70b2407d41187a475599edfba5b7647ea39252f24cc316eaf9984c1f895dad6bbcb43206f7222b71ed9eac4c84c382992af7903c831ceb4407261c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"maY7YkpZGqJmVhCURWwfqETeLY-qwyY-hQIaJUV_QGU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"kuPEc2Wr2AOWCjTB2Odep553BUM8Mht8S9lANqipBDk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\"